title: Ciena 5171 & 5142: Temperature
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/ciena
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors

 - the temperature in degrees celsius

 - the status of the device as reported by the device

 The check returns {CRIT} if the device reported status deviates from normal. Otherwise, the check
 returns {OK}.

 This check supports the Ciena 5171 Packetwave Platform and 5142 Service Aggregation Switch.

 The relevant MIBs are CIENA-CES-CHASSIS-MIB and WWP-LEOS-CHASSIS-MIB.
item:
 A unique id starting at 1.
discovery:
 One service is created for each port reporting a status and a temperature reading.
